2. Create a manual adjustment in Inventory → ADJUSTMENT row with reason appears
3. Navigate to `/inventory/movements` → rows display correctly with color-coded badges
4. Filter by product → only that product's movements show
5. Click CSV Export → file downloads with correct columns
